No. 11-6814. Assem A. Abulkhair, Petitioner v. Reuben Banks. 565 U.S. 1090, 132 S. Ct. 851,

181 L. Ed. 2d 546,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8909. December 12, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of New Jersey, Appellate Division, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
